OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1773951077
OL,3,CMan arrested for the rape and kidnap
OL,4,Cof a woman more than 30 years ago
OL,6,FA man has been arrested in Gloucester
OL,7,Ffor the rape and kidnap of a woman
OL,8,Fmore than three decades ago.
OL,10,FThe 69-year-old was arrested at a
OL,11,Fproperty on Wednesday 18 March on
OL,12,Fsuspicion of rape, kidnap, indecent
OL,13,Fassault, and assault occasioning
OL,14,Factual bodily harm.
OL,16,FOfficers from Gloucestershire Police
OL,17,Fare now carrying out a search of the
OL,18,Fproperty as part of the investigation.
OL,20,FThe offences were committed more than
OL,21,F35 years ago during the 1970s and 80s.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
