OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1773951077
OL,3,CMan arrested for the rape and kidnap
OL,4,Cof a woman more than 30 years ago
OL,6,FPolice say the victim has been
OL,7,Finformed of the arrest and has been
OL,8,Foffered access to specialist support
OL,9,Fservices.
OL,11,FThe man is currently in police custody
OL,12,Fwhere he will be interviewed by
OL,13,Fdetectives while further enquiries
OL,14,Ftake place.
OL,16,FDetective Chief Inspector Wayne Usher
OL,17,Fsaid: "These violent sexual offences
OL,18,Fwere committed over a sustained period
OL,19,Fand have had a lasting impact on the
OL,20,Fvictim.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
